\newlabel{fig:patch_catchbar}{{4.2}{59}{Patch-filter (v2) per-bucket confuser catch rate at \texttt {patch\_thr}=0.5, against the $0.90$ ``decisiveness'' bar. Helicopters ($71\%$) and birds ($64\%$) are mid; airplanes ($52\%$, median patch probability $0.540$) are the actionable gap. All three buckets sit below the bar, the motivation for the feature-reuse successor}{figure.caption.55}{}}
